---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Tree Services In Parrish, FL | Parrish Tree Removal"
  description="Explore tree removal, tree trimming, stump grinding, and storm cleanup services in Parrish, Florida."
>
  <section class="internal-hero">
    <div class="internal-hero-shell">
      <span class="eyebrow">Services</span>
      <h1>Tree service options for common property concerns</h1>
      <p>
        Explore the main project types homeowners ask about most often in Parrish and
        nearby communities.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request A Free Estimate</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="page-shell">
    <section class="page-section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2 class="section-title-reveal">Service Categories</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="service-grid">
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">🪵</div>
          <h3>Tree Removal</h3>
          <p>Projects involving damaged, unwanted, unstable, or awkwardly placed trees.</p>
          <a href="/tree-removal" class="service-link">Open Page</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌳</div>
          <h3>Tree Trimming</h3>
          <p>Pruning, shaping, branch reduction, and maintenance planning for growth control.</p>
          <a href="/tree-trimming" class="service-link">Open Page</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">🚜</div>
          <h3>Stump Grinding</h3>
          <p>Post-removal cleanup when a leftover stump still affects the yard.</p>
          <a href="/stump-grinding" class="service-link">Open Page</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">⛈️</div>
          <h3>Storm Cleanup</h3>
          <p>Tree and debris concerns after severe weather, broken limbs, or blocked access.</p>
          <a href="/emergency-tree-service" class="service-link">Open Page</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2 class="section-title-reveal">What Helps An Estimate</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="stack-grid">
        <article class="stack-panel">
          <h3>Location on the property</h3>
          <p>Let the request reflect whether the tree is near the roof, fence, driveway, or pool area.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="stack-panel">
          <h3>Project urgency</h3>
          <p>It is helpful to know whether the request is routine maintenance or a recent concern.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="stack-panel">
          <h3>Photos if available</h3>
          <p>Wide yard shots and close photos of the issue can make the next step much clearer.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
